Allow `.kaccess` to specify some caching behaviour, for the Kepler protocol.

Prevent users loading .kaccess

Cache `.kaccess` files against their URLs, so they don't have to be reloaded on
each request. This will have the downside of making it impossible to modify
them without restarting the server.

Make the listeners bind to specific network interfaces. At present, they bind
to all available interfaces.

Implement an access log

Implement an error log, rather than just logging to stderr.

